name: OneMoreTry
description:
Powered by PixelMonkey studio

Game Controls

W/S or Up/Down Arrows

This game is named "One more try" because of the reassurance you can do better next time.

It's meant to challenge your reflexes of perfectly avoiding the obstacles. 

! Good luck and have fun !

This is my first project ever so if you encounter bugs and want to report them or if you want to enhance the in-game experience with new creative ideas you can find my contact information directly in the game.
